{"tid":2146983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"近百人迎接旺角衝突最老抗爭者出獄 Sam 哥：我地欠後生","createTime":"2020-08-09T03:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T03:08:57.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf900a91aa68f841b43ac62f5792aa1da668cad","tid":2146983,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:00:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%8E%E6%8E%A5%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%9C%80%E8%80%81%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%84-sam-%E5%93%A5-%E6%88%91%E5%9C%B0%E6%AC%A0%E5%BE%8C%E7%94%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BF%258E%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E6%259C%2580%25E8%2580%2581%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258D%2584-sam-%25E5%2593%25A5-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%2594%259F%2F&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=61fd3e60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BF%258E%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E6%259C%2580%25E8%2580%2581%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258D%2584-sam-%25E5%2593%25A5-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%2594%259F%2F&h=b8a3961b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%8E%E6%8E%A5%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%9C%80%E8%80%81%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E5%87%BA%E7%8D%84-sam-%E5%93%A5-%E6%88%91%E5%9C%B0%E6%AC%A0%E5%BE%8C%E7%94%9F/</a><br />\n<br />\n8.8　大欖懲教所<br />\n近百人迎接旺角衝突最老抗爭者 Sam 哥出獄<br />\nSam 哥：我地欠後生仔<br />\n<br />\n弁言<br />\n<br />\n著名的英國詩人奧登（Wystan Hugh Auden）來過香港。時值 1938 年日本侵華，彼時廣州戰事正酣，隨後香港也相繼淪陷。奧登特為香港賦詩一首，結尾道：<br />\n<br />\nTen thousand miles from home and What&rsquo;s-Her-Name<br />\nThe bugle on the Late Victorian hill<br />\nPuts out the soldier&rsquo;s light; off-stage, a war<br />\n<br />\nThuds like the slamming of a distant door:<br />\nWe cannot postulate a General Will;<br />\nFor what we are, we have ourselves to blame.<br />\n<br />\n辭家萬里不知伊人芳名何姓<br />\n入夜維多利亞山上的號角響起<br />\n將士熄滅營火；戰爭在台下悄悄登場<br />\n<br />\n炮火就恍如遠處的敲門聲：<br />\n豈敢問天人間何嘗有命；<br />\n我們是誰，祇能怪我們自己。<br />\n<br />\n這首詩隔世預言香港和 Sam 哥的生命：我們的共同意志 / 天命（General Will），總要在反覆的淪陷下畢生尋覓。"},{"pid":"79c2ae4bf04bce891e59e9e74692a687944563db","tid":2146983,"uid":1096,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"他仍記在 2015 年的旺角，譚得志（快必）罵一些戴口罩的年輕人為「鬼」，便是一次顯例。「你憑咩嘢話鬼？人地要返工唔可以俾老細見到。佢到而家都未道過歉，依方面我好執著，你傷害咗人地，一日唔道歉我一日都唔會原諒。唔係記仇唔係私怨，而係針對做法。我好反感泛民打壓後生仔依啲陋習。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54500bd2edcb58bf39c242596f5485733ebe023","tid":2146983,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79c2ae4bf04bce891e59e9e74692a687944563db","tid":2146983,"uid":1096,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"他仍記在 2015 年的旺角，譚得志（快必）罵一些戴口罩的年輕人為「鬼」，便是一次顯例。「你憑咩嘢話鬼？人地要返工唔可以俾老細見到。佢到而家都未道過歉，依方面我好執著，你傷害咗人地，一日唔道歉我一日都唔會原諒。唔係記仇唔係私怨，而係針對做法。我好反感泛民打壓後生仔依啲陋習。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}